OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start in the far west,
OL,6,Fotherwise rather grey with the odd
OL,7,Fspot of light rain. Skies however
OL,8,Fturning brighter this afternoon with
OL,9,Fsome sunshine developing later from
OL,10,Fthe east. Feeling cooler than
OL,11,Fyesterday with a brisk easterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine evening with plenty of
OL,14,Flate sunshine developing. A few mist
OL,15,Fand fog patches forming overnight but
OL,16,Fmost remaining clear. Turning chilly
OL,17,Fin the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
