OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny early mist and fog
OL,6,Fquickly clearing leaving a fine and
OL,7,Fsunny day. Remaining breezy,
OL,8,Fespecially in the south, but feeling a
OL,9,Flittle warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FRemaining dry, sunny and warm on
OL,13,FThursday. Sunshine increasingly hazy
OL,14,Fon Friday with a risk of showers but
OL,15,Fremaining warm and increasingly humid.
OL,16,FFresher on Saturday with further
OL,17,Fshowers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
